*Catfish Creek in [[Algoma District, Ontario|Algoma District]], a tributary of the [[Magpie River (Ontario)|Magpie River]] that flows into [[Lake Superior]] at [[Wawa, Ontario|Wawa]] <ref>{{cite cgndb|id= FDJYC|title=Catfish Creek|accessdate= 2011-01-23}}</ref> *[[Catfish Creek (Lake Erie)]] in Elgin County, that flows into Lake Erie at Port Bruce *Catfish Creek in [[Norfolk County, Ontario|Norfolk County]], a tributary of the [[Black Creek (Ontario)|Black Creek]], which in turn flows into Lake Erie at [[Port Dover, Ontario|Port Dover]]<ref>{{cite cgndb|id= FDJYB|title=Catfish Creek|accessdate= 2011-01-23}}</ref>
